    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Rough but complete older example being sold as-is as a project, parts car, or very budget-minded driver. This is not a show car and not something I would describe as sorted; expect significant cosmetic wear, aged paint, interior deterioration, and likely mechanical needs before it can be fully enjoyed or relied on. Best suited for someone who wants an inexpensive entry point and is prepared to put time and money into repairs and recommissioning.",
