    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Mint-condition car that presents exceptionally well inside and out. It appears to have been extremely well cared for, with a clean, well-kept interior, strong exterior finish, and the kind of overall fit and presentation buyers hope to find in a top-quality example. It runs and drives excellent, and a buyer can expect a car that is ready to enjoy immediately with very little to nitpick beyond the minor signs of careful use you might expect on any driven vehicle.",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
